    "description": "Japaniace Co.,Ltd. engages in the advanced engineering business in Japan. The company offers on-site development support and contract development; software design, development, testing, operation, and maintenance services for the IT, communications, and manufacturing industries; network and server design and construction, operation, and maintenance services for telecommunications carriers, finance, distribution, and government agencies; and mechanical and electrical design of products and equipment for the automotive, office automation, digital equipment, and robotics sectors. It also engages in advanced technology services, including Al, IoT, and cloud computing; research, development, and analytical support services for chemical, pharmaceutical, cosmetics, food, and material manufacturers, as well as the academia, public institutions, and contract testing companies; dispatch of engineers in specialized fields; job placement services for the real estate, facilities, and construction industries; and educational services. In addition, the company is involved in the development and software evaluation of web systems and applications, business and financial systems, and public institution systems; virtual infrastructure construction and operation; system operation and maintenance; security response; system implementation and migration support; function addition and customization; integration with other systems; design and construction of AWS, Azure, and GCP environments; cloud migration support; chemical testing, analysis, and measurement; bio cell and genetic experiments; research and analysis using natural language processing; and inspection and analysis using image processing. Japaniace Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Yokohama, Japan."
